      <title>独家：消息人士称瑞银关闭部分中国私募基金并将裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-shuts-some-china-private-funds-will-lay-off-staff-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位直接了解情况的消息人士称，瑞银正在关闭部分中国私募基金业务，并将裁员三分之一的员工，以削减在华运营成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-shuts-some-china-private-funds-will-lay-off-staff-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:42:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
